Hi all,

For today, since boost 1.83 has been introduced into stable,
there were a couple of packages that needed timely fixes with
the new version of that library, otherwise they would fail to
build from source.  These packages were:

  * bali-phy, affected by #1056087 (and also double build bug
    #1043647),
  * autodock-vina, affected by #1056089,
  * rsem, affected by #1056010 (and duplicate #1056011).

There were also a couple of supplementary double build bugs in
the pot:

  * cassiopee, affected by #1043792,
  * libgo-perl, affected by #1046227.

Have a nice day,  :)
